Below is the list of all my Commands & Modules!

`!`| ship - Ship two members :heart:
`!`| dog - Send dog photo!
`!`| cat - Send cat photo!
`!`| ngif - Send anime gif!
`!`| poke - Poke mentioned member
`!`| hug - Hug mentioned member
`!`| kiss - Kiss someone ^^
`!`| pat - Pat someone uwu
`!`| feed - Feed somenone :3
`!`| cuddle - Cuddle someone 0w0
`!`| slap - Slap someone ;-;
`!`| tickle - Tickle someone >w<
`!`| owoify - What this command does is replace all the "Ls" and "Rs" in your sent message into "Ws" and other stuff like changing exclaimation points into kawaii textmojis to make you sound weawwy adowwable!
`!`| kill - Kill someone O.O

**`-.-`**

**__▸MODERATION ― RELATED!__** 
`!`| kick ― KICK THE MENTIONED USER!
`!`| ban ― BAN THE MENTIONED USER! 
`!`| clear ― CLEARS THE DEFINED MESSAGES!

**`-.-`**

**__▸USEFUL ― RELATED!__** 
`!`| malsearch anime or manga [title] - Send anime or manga information
`!`| mc ― Makes minecraft achievements with yout text
`!`| osu - Send your osu profile
`!`| invite - Send bot invite
`!`| meme - Send random meme
`!`| avatar - Send member avatar
